-- http-integration.fl — HTTP fetch, JSON parsing, type conversion
-- Demonstrates: Fetch URL, Post to URL, parsed as JSON, converted to number
-- Run: fluent run examples/http-integration.fl

Output "═══════════════════════════════════════".
Output "  HTTP Integration Demo".
Output "═══════════════════════════════════════".
Output "".

-- ── Fetch a public API ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "── Fetch: Public JSON API ──".

Try to fetch "https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1" and call the result post_response.
If that fails, let post_response be a record with status 503 ok false body "Offline".

Output post_response.
Output "".

-- ── Parse the response body ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "── Parse & Extract ──".

If post_response.ok is true:
    Let post_body be the result of post_response.body.
    Output post_body.
Otherwise, Output "  Could not fetch post — working offline.".

Output "".

-- ── Type conversion pipeline ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "── Type Conversions ──".

Let raw_values be a list containing "42", "3.14", "100", "7".

For each raw in raw_values:
    Let as_num be the result of raw converted to number.
    Let doubled be as_num plus as_num.
    Output doubled.
End loop.

Output "".

-- ── JSON round-trip ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "── JSON Ops ──".

Let payload be a record with
    model "claude-sonnet-4-6"
    temperature 0.7
    max_tokens 1024.

Output payload.

-- ── String pipeline ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "".
Output "── String Pipeline ──".

Let title be "  FLUENT Natural Language Programming Language  ".
Let cleaned be the result of trim title.
Let slug be the result of slugify cleaned.
Let words be the result of split cleaned by " ".
Let word_count be the result of the word count of cleaned.

Output slug.
Output word_count.

-- ── Math pipeline ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Output "".
Output "── Math Pipeline ──".

Let raw_score be 87.456789.
Let rounded be the result of round raw_score to 2 decimal places.
Let percentage be the result of round raw_score to 0 decimal places.
Output rounded.
Output percentage.

Let prices be a list containing 19.99, 49.99, 9.99, 99.99, 29.99.
Let total_price be the result of the sum of prices.
Let avg_price be the result of the average of prices.
Let min_price be the result of the minimum of prices.
Let max_price be the result of the maximum of prices.

Output total_price.
Output avg_price.
Output min_price.
Output max_price.

Output "".
Output "═══════════════════════════════════════".
Output "  HTTP integration demo complete.".
Output "═══════════════════════════════════════".
